reviewText: There are several sexy girls in this DVD, as usual on Peach DVDs, but Heather Vandeven makes me nearly forget the others in this one, (Heather Carolin isn't bad in it). I think this DVD surely has Heather Vandeven's sexiest scenes. The scene with her and the pizza delivery boy is one I can watch over and over, and she has some other good ones too. It just occurred to me that she reminds me of a cute blonde from the Netherlands I dated in college. My "Freddy" and Heather are the sexiest Dutch blondes I've ever seen.
